<div class="title">Born Again</div>
<div class="substance">2C-T-2</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Arrowhead&Exact=1">Arrowhead</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Arrowhead. "Born Again: An Experience with 2C-T-2 (exp36175)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Feb 1, 2005. erowid.org/exp/36175</div>

<br/>



